                        </div>
                        <p dir="ltr" data-ogsc="rgb(117, 117, 117)"><em>Delegate Marcia S. "Cia" Price serves the 95th District in the Virginia House of Delegates. As a member of the General Laws Committee, she has proposed housing justice legislation for several years, fighting for renters' rights and eviction prevention. She has been serving since 2016 and is a Secretary of the Virginia Legislative Black Caucus.</em></p>
